28. Real Production Architecture
In real companies:
Authentication
    ├ LDAP
    ├ HTPasswd
    └ OAuth providers

Authorization
    ├ cluster-admin
    ├ admin
    ├ edit
    └ view
Users → Groups → Roles → Permissions.


